				<h3 class="mt-4">관리자 정보 변경</h3>
				<div class="container" style="max-width: 550px;">
					<div class="mt-5 row ">
						<h5 class="col-3 ml-1 mr-5 ">아이디 </h5>
						<span class="border-b col-6 ml-1 pb-2 id-span">dDragon</span>
